                      |Stay tuned with us. We post out new exciting projects here.
              li.work.vox
                .desc-container.vox
                  .icon-container
                    img(src="/images/icn_vox.png")
                  .text-container
                    p.desc.font-roboto
                      |VOX is a unique concept 
                      |<br />application where you can share
                      |12-sec recordings of your life story.
                    p.url.font-roboto
                      a.vox(href="http://voxstory.com", target="_blank") voxstory.com
                .image-container.vox
                  .image-area.vox
                    img.vox(src="/images/vox1.png")
                    img.vox(src="/images/vox2.png")
                    img.vox(src="/images/vox3.png")
              li.work.minam
                .desc-container.minam
                  .icon-container
                    img(src="/images/icn_minam.png")
                  .text-container
                    p.desc.font-roboto.
                      This application is mean. You can compete with your friends to find out who is the ugliest one.
                    p.url.font-roboto
                      a.minam(href="http://minam.easi6.com", target="_blank") minam.easi6.com
                .image-container.minam
                  .image-area.minam
                    img.minam(src="/images/minam.png")
              li.work.tomoni
                .desc-container.tomoni
                  .icon-container
                    img(src="/images/icn_tomoni.png")
                  .text-container
                    p.desc.font-roboto.
                      Tomoni is an application where you can broadcast and participate in activities near you. Don’t play alone, play together with Tomoni.
                    p.url.font-roboto
                      a.tomoni(href="http://tomoniapp.com", target="_blank") tomoniapp.com
                .image-container.tomoni
                  .image-area.tomoni
                    img.tomoni(src="/images/tomoni1.png")
                    img.tomoni(src="/images/tomoni2.png")
                    img.tomoni(src="/images/tomoni3.png")
              li.work.dnd
                .desc-container.dnd
                  .icon-container
                    img(src="/images/icn_dnd.png")
                  .text-container
                    p.desc.font-roboto.
                      The fastest and easiest way to meet your friends is Doors & Dots. 
                    p.url.font-roboto
                      a.vox(href="http://doorsndots.com", target="_blank") doorsndots.com
                .video-container.dnd
                  .video-area.dnd
                    iframe(src="//player.vimeo.com/video/72255740", frameborder="0", webkitallowfullscreen, mozallowfullscreen, allowfullscreen)

        //div.work-images.hidden-xs
